#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:20
msgid "This tool allows you to choose a point from the canvas and make the color of that point the active foreground color. When a painting or drawing tool is selected the Color Sampler tool can also be quickly accessed by pressing the :kbd:`Ctrl` key."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
